{"tid":2448184,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"扮Pixel恩物：Another Widget","createTime":"2021-03-15T17:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T14:25:16.000Z","uid":40118,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"68a32b9c4f21cd677780304f4f0b6b29ae27f027","tid":2448184,"uid":40118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T17:31:19.000Z","msg":"用慣Pixel launcher, 好鐘意佢既at a glance 功能，好精簡咁係畫面顯示時間天氣下個約會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/coeQZ4d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcoeQZ4d.png&h=719729bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實佢只係個google 提供既widget. 係S21 其實都有。但係唔係用緊pixel 既話，個widget 就只識顯示時間天氣，唔識顯示calendar event. <br />\n<br />\n後來終於搵到個替代品： Another Widget<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tommasoberlose.anotherwidget\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.tommasoberlose.anotherwidget&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirLtp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=7628a6c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.tommasoberlose.anotherwidget</a><br />\n<br />\n- Open source project, 唔駛錢，但接受捐款<br />\n- 做到幾乎同google 既 at a glance widget 幾乎一樣，可以睇到下個event. <br />\n- 但係要睇到天氣既設定就麻煩D，要搵個天氣資料API 開個account, 打個API key 落去。但係set 好左就唔駛再理。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KiuYpxG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKiuYpxG.png&h=8eb49a88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯一缺點係無正體中文localization, 只有殘體，重要譯錯哂。我打算submit 一份正體中文localization 畀原作者。或者可以做多一個香港話版localization (cn-rHK)..."},{"pid":"2a22c1ebd981349871a114607c17fbb300ee13d6","tid":2448184,"uid":122769,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:22:30.000Z","msg":"我唔係用緊pixel, 但係個google widget 都可以顯示埋行事曆活動<br />\n可能你有啲嘢Set漏咗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m8TKn3p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm8TKn3p.jpg&h=8d35d374&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1f32c2066310265fc9f310f9cbea22d59e7466a4","tid":2448184,"uid":78304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T03:20:29.000Z","msg":"我直情想熄左行事曆阻住我睇時間<br />\n無得揀， 唯有唔用行事曆"},{"pid":"96c41bef07f60cfc9b9ae06cfe8c3ec7f49f976d","tid":2448184,"uid":40118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a22c1ebd981349871a114607c17fbb300ee13d6","tid":2448184,"uid":122769,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:22:30.000Z","msg":"我唔係用緊pixel, 但係個google widget 都可以顯示埋行事曆活動<br />\n可能你有啲嘢Set漏咗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m8TKn3p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm8TKn3p.jpg&h=8d35d374&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:59:54.000Z","msg":"我同時拎住pixel 2 xl 同 s21 實驗過。<br />\npixel launcher 既 setting 入面有得揀at a glance 顯示乜嘢。用其他launcher 就無呢個setting."},{"pid":"0ff9f8e4aa3432a721cb36d92c6fb11fb9811ace","tid":2448184,"uid":140167,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2a22c1ebd981349871a114607c17fbb300ee13d6","tid":2448184,"uid":122769,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:22:30.000Z","msg":"我唔係用緊pixel, 但係個google widget 都可以顯示埋行事曆活動<br />\n可能你有啲嘢Set漏咗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m8TKn3p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm8TKn3p.jpg&h=8d35d374&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:25:16.000Z","msg":"女全相？"}]}